snippet.title: Bodycam - Early Access Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
JOIN THE PLAYTEST / JOIN THE CREW : https://reissad.com/Crew

💥 Bodycam will be releasing publicly in early access on Steam on 11:00 PM UTC ,June 7
💥Bodycam Playtest is LIVE NOW

- The whole team is eager to see everybody's reaction to the game for the very first time! 

Song Name: Slowboy, lucaf. - U Bitcrushed My Heart
